org.sureassert.uc.annotation

Annotation Type IgnoreTestCoverage


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={TYPE,METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR})
public @interface IgnoreTestCoverage
    Prevents Sureassert UC gathering or reporting any test coverage data for the annotated class, method or constructor.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nathan Dolan
